<type>(<scope>): <English summary> / <中文摘要>

English:
- What changed.
- Why it changed.
- User or developer impact.

中文:
- 修改了什么。
- 为什么修改。
- 对用户或开发者的影响。

Validation:
- Exact commands or checks run.
- Any checks intentionally not run, with reason.

Commit Discipline:
- This commit represents one validated change batch.
- Follow-up implementation starts only after this commit is recorded.
